data.description: Huge benefit to a potential buyer; the seller has an assumable VA Loan of $128,000 at a 3.125% interest rate. Location is everything! This 4 bedroom, 3.5 bath home is nestled on a large corner within walking distance to Sandy Beach, Greers Ferry Lake, and Heber Springs schools. Featuring brand new roof and a true split floor plan, it has a master suite that will check all of your boxes and a cathedral-style living room with a large kitchen and dining room. Lots of updates throughout. Schedule your showing today!
